Program Purpose:
---------------
    A program that gathers key travel data in one place and uses AI to turn
    a provided location and dates to a clear travel guide wth tour attractions
    and items to pack provided. Also gives travel deals to assist in helping someone
    pick out a location


Compile/run:
-----------

   python3 unit_tests.py for unit_tests
   python3 main.py to run functions

Files:
-----

    unit_tests.py: Unit tests for project
    exchange_rates.py - Compares exchange rates over a specified time using Exchange Rate API
    serp_flights_deals.py - Get flight deals from Serp API Google Flights and returns the best deal with travel information
    gen.py - Uses Gemini Google AI Studio API to prompt an itinerary for a given location and date

    README: This file